data.description: Discover your dream home! This 4-bed, 2.5-bath 2-story gem boasts a spacious lot with no rear neighbors. Enjoy the open concept living with 2 downstairs living areas, an additional upstairs living space, and a delightful enclosed sunroom to catch those stunning sunsets. Plus, you're just minutes from major shopping centers, restaurants, and more. Don't wait, schedule a showing today!
